description: Welcome to 433 W 4th Street #2, a bright and spacious two-bedroom condo in Southie. Spread over two levels, this home features a large living room with a gas fireplace, an oversized eat-in kitchen, and a convenient half bath on the main floor. Upstairs, you’ll find two sunny bedrooms, a full bath, and in-unit laundry. Tucked away on a quiet, tree-lined street with tons of natural light throughout. Move in and enjoy all that South Boston has to offer.
